{
  "stem": "13096.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 477.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "We were just waiting because now, and every two hours or so, they will tell us stop.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We will stop five seconds or five minutes, and we'd carry on.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But now, they say stop, while they were talking.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And we still-- we were stopping.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And waiting and waiting and waiting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Come 4 o'clock, come 5 o'clock, and then it was dawn and we can see around.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "They would look around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "We see not a single German around us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "They all ran in all direction and they left us in the queue.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "So when it was-- we're about 200 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "When it was, you know, dawn-- and these other prisoners, they were all Polish, and all these, they knew all the land and their surroundings because Auschwitz is, you know, in the Polish border, you know, with Russia, whatever.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And then, they knew their land.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "We didn't know a thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they all run and they left us standing-- us, we're speaking Spanish-- myself, my sister, another girl from Rhodes Island, two French girls, one Greek girl-- Salonika-- and one man that he was limping.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was also an old man that we knew.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was not limping when he arrived at the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was nice and strong.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But at the time there, he was limping.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The rest-- they abandoned us in the snow.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we look over all direction.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There we no Germans.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What we can do?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If the Germans came back, they would have found us there standing like little lambs to take it away again.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, we look where to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We saw in a place, there was a little hut.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We went towards that little hut.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we went there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was empty.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was nobody there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we saw a fire going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
